CatDescriptText: Cutline of related image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, April 28, 1956, pg. A29 reads: "Listen Attentively - Delegates to the Youth Conference held at the Centre Avenue YMCA last week-end listen attentively as the Rev. Virgil D. Moccia, of Bidwell Presbyterian Church, speaks to them. Over 100 young people attended. - Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: Group of young men and women, including young man wearing solid colored suit jacket, holding fork to young woman seated across from him, seated at banquet tables in Centre Avenue YMCA for youth lyceum conference
